Feature: Hotel Booking In Adactin Application

Scenario: user Going To Login The Adactin Hotel 
Given user Will Launch The Url 
When enter The Name In The Username Field
And enter The Password In The Password Field
Then click The Login Button To Get In The Homepage

Scenario: user Wants To Fill All The Field In The Search Hotel Page
When select The Location In the Location Field
And select The Hotel In The Hotels Field
And select The Room Type In The Room Type Field
And select The Numbers Of Room In The Number Room Field
And enter The Date In The Check In Date Field
And enter The Date In The Check Out Date Field
And select The Adults Per Room In The Adults Per Room Field
And select The Children Per Room In The Children Per Room Field
Then click The Search Button For The Next page

Scenario: user Want To Fill The Select Hotel Page
When click The Check Box In The Check Box Field
Then click The Continue Button For The Next Page

Scenario: user Need To Fill All The field In The Book Hotel Page
When enter The Name In The First Name Field
And enter The Last Name In The Last Name Field
And enter The Address In The Billing Address Field
And enter The Credit Card Number In The Credit Card No Field
And select The Credit Card Type In The Credit Card Type   
And select The Month And Year In The Expiry Date Field 
And enter The CVV Number In The CVV Number Field
Then click The Book Now Button

Scenario: user Going To Logout the Page
Then click The Logout Button












    
 